📱 QR Code Generator

A simple and responsive QR Code Generator built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.


---

🚀 Features

✅ Generate QR codes in real-time

✅ Clean dark-themed UI

✅ Input any text or URL

✅ Error handling for empty input

✅ Lightweight & responsive


---

📂 Project Structure

qr-code-generator/
│── index.html   # Main HTML file  
│── style.css    # Styling (dark theme UI)  
│── script.js    # QR code generation logic


---

⚙️ Setup & Usage

1. Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/bhoopesh5/QR-code-generator.git
cd qr-code-generator


2. Open index.html in your browser.


3. Enter text or a URL in the input box, click Generate QR, and your QR code will appear instantly.




---

📚 Technologies Used

HTML5 – Structure

CSS3 – Styling & layout

JavaScript (QRCode.js) – QR code generation



---

✨ Future Improvements

